  "title": "Tracing / Tally Clerk",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Tallying of import and export cargoes</li>\n  <li>Liaising with Haulier, customer and office personnel</li>\n  <li>Coordinating with various functions as required</li>\n  <li>Assist with stock count</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Levels, no need experience</li>\n  <li>Preferably able to read, write and understand English for better coordination</li>\n  <li>Able to work under pressure/stress</li>\n  <li>Preferred knowledge of cargoes</li>\n  <li>Computer literacy</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills</li>\n  <li>Immediate vacancy</li>\n</ul>",
